title: BMW Road Map Europe Business 2014
description:
This DVD set is ( SA 606 ) to be used exclusively for the BMW Navigation system Business in conjunction with a MASK ( Multi Audio System Controller ) 

Navigation data compatible with following vehicles (SA606) 
E60,E61: 08.2003-05.2010 
E81,E82,E83,E84: 06.2004-09.2009 
E90,E91,E92,E93: 03.2005-09.2008 

Update the business product consists of two panes. The first disc contains the previously known Western European 
Countries . The second DVD includes, among other things, the new Eastern European countries . The division looks in detail as follows: 

DVD 1 : 
Andorra, Austria, Belgium , Denmark, Germany , Finland , France, 
Greece , Gibraltar, Great Britain, Ireland , Italy, 
Liechtenstein , Luxembourg , Monaco, Netherlands , Norway, 
Austria , Portugal, San Marino, Slovak Republic, Spain, 
Sweden , Switzerland , Czech Republic , Vatican City . 

DVD 2: 
Denmark, Germany , Finland, Greece , Italy , Croatia, 
Liechtenstein , Norway, Austria , Poland , San Marino, 
Sweden , Switzerland , Slovakia , Slovenia, Czech 
Republic , Hungary , Vatican City .

more info 

    Free TMC service is not available in all countries. For the reception of the encrypted TMC service we offer country-specific to a BMW ConnectedDrive contract . 
    2D map view in addition to the arrow display (only new vehicles from 03 /2007) 
    Directory of BMW partners 
    POI database with 32 categories 

Changes to the Business in 2014 
This update contains a cover increase by 680 089 kilometers and 29,990,641 additional new addresses, 1,203,329 additional POIs
